data.description: This beautifully remodeled gem, is waiting for you to make it your own. With three spacious bedrooms and two elegant bathrooms, this residence offers both comfort and style. The heart of the home is a stunning kitchen, designed with a modern touch and equipped with all the amenities you desire. Enjoy your morning coffee in the charming breakfast nook, with abundant natural light pouring in. The great location in the Autumn Ridge subdivision not only provides a peaceful and friendly neighborhood but also places you within easy reach of the bustling 1604, offering convenience for your daily commute. Plus, you'll be close to the luxurious shopping and dining options at The Shops at La Cantera. This is your chance to experience the perfect blend of modern living in a sought-after location - don't miss out!
